# SDLC Skills — Architect

## Your Skills (17)

### Design & Planning
- `/design-review [file-or-'full']` — Review architecture and design patterns
- `/plan-gen specs/NNN/spec.md` — Generate implementation plan from approved spec
- `/impact-analysis <file-or-feature>` — Blast radius analysis for proposed changes
- `/plan-merge specs/*/plan.md` — Merge multiple plans into unified execution plan
- `/reverse-engineer full` — Reverse-engineer codebase into full technical docs

### Specification
- `/spec-gen '<feature>'` — Generate structured technical specification
- `/spec-review specs/NNN/spec.md` — Validate implementation matches spec
- `/spec-evolve revise specs/NNN/spec.md` — Version a spec with amendments
- `/feature-balance-sheet deep specs/NNN/spec.md` — Full cost-benefit portfolio analysis

### Architecture Health
- `/tech-debt-audit full` — Codebase health check
- `/code-ownership-mapper risks` — Map ownership, knowledge silos, bus factor
- `/api-contract-analyzer main` — Detect breaking API changes
- `/migration-tracker status` — Track migration progress

### Decision Support
- `/decision-log capture specs/NNN/spec.md` — Capture decision rationale
- `/gate-briefing specs/NNN/ --audience engineering` — Gate decision briefing
- `/quality-gate spec-to-plan specs/NNN/spec.md` — Stage gate enforcement
- `/report-trends all` — Trend analysis across reports

## Your Pipelines (3)

### Design to Plan
Spec → implementation plan with quality gates:
```
/run-pipeline architect/design-to-plan specs/NNN/spec.md
```
Chain: design-review → plan-gen → quality-gate → decision-log

### System Health
Architectural health assessment:
```
/run-pipeline architect/system-health
```
Chain: tech-debt-audit → code-ownership-mapper → api-contract-analyzer → report-trends

### Migration Planning
Plan a technical migration:
```
/run-pipeline architect/migration-planning '<migration description>'
```
Chain: migration-tracker → impact-analysis → plan-gen → plan-merge
